title: Rocket From The Crypt - Born In 69 (Live): Converse Represent SF
description:
Converse Represent San Francisco closed with a punk-inspired night of epic proportions, headlined by So-Cal legends Rocket From The Crypt and Suicidal Tendencies. Following up raucous performances from The Shrine, Ceremony, and The Bronx -- the packed house crowd was treated to a rare performance from RFTC in full regalia. They kicked off their set with a classic - "Born in '69." - and the diehards in the crowd absolutely lost it. 

The Converse San Francisco store is now open. Come check it out at 838 Market St!
